code: export class ColorUtils{static makeColorHex(color){return'#'+color;}static makeColorNumberHex(color){let val=color.toString(16);if(val.length<6){const diff=6-val.length;for(let i=0;i<diff;i++){val='0'+val;}}return'#'+val;}static convertFromHex(color){return parseInt(color.replace('#',''),16);}}
